-c3359829210="" class="presented-response-container ng-tns-c3359829210-42" jslog="283401;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="2"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3359829210-42"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3359829210-42"><!----><thinking-overlay _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c123358160="" class="enable-luminous-fast-follows ng-star-inserted"><!----></thinking-overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted">Gemini ha dicho</h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2691161566="" data-message-id="msg-1784851430120-0" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_67445f5c922ca2a8" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_67445f5c922ca2a8" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><h3 data-path-to-node="0">🌳 ¿Por qué no cambia el gráfico visual del árbol?</h3><p data-path-to-node="1">En el video se observa que la información de la tarjeta azul y el título cambian perfectamente (de <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="99">1. Semilla</code> a <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="112">2. Brote Menor</code> y <code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="129">3. Brote Explorador</code>). Sin embargo, el árbol visual se queda estático.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">Esto sucede por dos razones técnicas en el código actual:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="3"><li><p data-path-to-node="3,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">URLs de Lottie Repetidas o Caídas:</b> En el diccionario <code data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="53">mapeo_bio</code>, las fases 4 a la 10 comparten exactamente la misma URL de animación (<code data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="133">[https://lottie.host/a6133a88](https://lottie.host/a6133a88)...</code>). Además, si alguna URL falla o no carga a tiempo, Streamlit entra en la cláusula <code data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="279">else</code> y dibuja el árbol verde 3D estándar que estás viendo.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Key de Animación Estática:</b> Cuando usas <code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="39">st_lottie</code>, si no cambia el parámetro <code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="76">key</code> o el JSON de forma clara, Streamlit reutiliza el componente cacheado de la primera animación renderizada.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="5">🛠️ Solución Definitiva (Garantizar Cambio de Ícono)</h3><p data-path-to-node="6">Para asegurar que cada fase cambie visualmente en pantalla, reemplazamos temporalmente las URLs externas de Lottie por <b data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="119">emojis vectoriales gigantes e íconos estilizados definidos por fase</b> en la función de renderizado. De esta manera, el cambio visual será instantáneo y 100% garantizado al simular.</p><h4 data-path-to-node="7">Código de Reemplazo en <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="23">frontend/app.py</code></h4><p data-path-to-node="8">Ubica la sección del <b data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="21">Visor Gráfico del Árbol</b> y reemplaza la asignación del diccionario y renderizado por este bloque limpio:</p><response-element class="no-md" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3875502131="" class="ng-tns-c3875502131-71 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3875502131-71 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_67445f5c922ca2a8&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,&quot;rc_d60ed04849c890de&quot;,null,null,&quot;es&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" style="display: block;" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ6AE"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3875502131-71"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3875502131-71"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-emphasized-body-m ng-tns-c3875502131-71 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="ng-tns-c3875502131-71">Python</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3875502131-71 ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" tabindex="-1" type="onSurface" size="small" fonticonname="arrow_circle_down" theme="lm" arialabel="Descargar código" gemtooltip="Descargar código" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c3875502131-71 gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2005957155="" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-35" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" maticonbutton="" matbadgeposition="after" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-badge mat-unthemed _mat-animation-noopable mat-badge-overlap mat-badge-above mat-badg