h-to-node="13,5,0" data-index-in-node="19">✨</code> (Luz cósmica)</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="14">Guarda los cambios, actualiza en GitHub (<code data-path-to-node="14" data-index-in-node="41">git push origin master</code>) y comprueba el cambio instantáneo al simular las fases.</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-footer complete gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><election-info-disclaimer _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c81433311="" style="display: none;" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></election-info-disclaimer><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3877821886="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3359829210-42 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" footer="" class="hide-on-print ng-tns-c36277369-43 hide-action-bar ng-tns-c3359829210-42 ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c36277369=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-43"><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-43 ng-star-inserted"><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" _nghost-ng-c3123964857="" class="ng-tns-c36277369-43 luminous-theme ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3123964857="" tabindex="-1" theme="lm" type="onSurface" arialabel="Buena respuesta" gemtooltip="Buena respuesta" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c200