t-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><gem-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" _nghost-ng-c1721858669=""><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1721858669="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate lm-icon-l lumi-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="arrow_circle_down" data-mat-icon-namespace="lumi-symbols" fonticon="arrow_circle_down"></mat-icon><!----><!----><!----></gem-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></gem-icon-button><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" tabindex="-1" type="onSurface" size="small" fonticonname="copy" theme="lm" arialabel="Copiar código" gemtooltip="Copiar código" data-test-id="gem-copy-button" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger copy-button ng-tns-c3875502131-72 gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2005957155="" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-36" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" maticonbutton="" matbadgeposition="after" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-badge mat-unthemed _mat-animation-noopable mat-badge-overlap mat-badge-above mat-badge-after mat-badge-small mat-badge-hidden ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-label="Copiar código" jslog="179062;track:generic_click,impression;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_d055fada06c6e1f6&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,&quot;rc_4db7ed067609ab7e&quot;,null,null,&quot;es&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]];mutable:true"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><gem-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" _nghost-ng-c1721858669=""><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1721858669="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate lm-icon-l lumi-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="copy" data-mat-icon-namespace="lumi-symbols" fonticon="copy"></mat-icon><!----><!----><!----></gem-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></gem-icon-button><!----><!----><!----><!----></div><!----><!----></div><!----><pre _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="ng-tns-c3875502131-72"><code _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" role="text" data-test-id="code-content" class="code-container formatted ng-tns-c3875502131-72">@<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> off
<span class="hljs-built_in">title</span> Historias que Inspiran® - Despliegue Automatico
<span class="hljs-built_in">color</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>A

<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> ========================================================
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span>   HISTORIAS QUE INSPIRAN (R) - DESPLIEGUE EN LA NUBE
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> ========================================================
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span>.

:: <span class="hljs-number">1</span>. Ir a la carpeta <span class="hljs-built_in">del</span> proyecto
<span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> /d "%~dp0"

:: <span class="hljs-number">2</span>. Preguntar el mensaje <span class="hljs-built_in">del</span> commit (Opcional)
<span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> /p commit_msg="Introduce la descripcion <span class="hljs-built_in">del</span> cambio (presiona ENTER para usar la por defecto): "

<span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> "<span class="hljs-variable">%commit_msg%</span>"=="" (
    <span class="hljs-built_in">set</span> commit_msg="update: actualizacion automatica de la plataforma"
)

<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span>.
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> [<span class="hljs-number">1</span>/<span class="hljs-number">3</span>] Guardando cambios en Git...
git add .

<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> [<span class="hljs-number">2</span>/<span class="hljs-number">3</span>] Creando punto de restauracion (Commit)...
git commit -m "<span class="hljs-variable">%commit_msg%</span>"

<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> [<span class="hljs-number">3</span>/<span class="hljs-number">3</span>] Subiendo cambios a la nube (GitHub / Streamlit Cloud / Render)...
git push origin master

<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span>.
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> ========================================================
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span>   ¡DESPLIEGUE EXITOSO! LA WEB SE ACTUALIZARA EN SEGUNDOS.
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span> ========================================================
<span class="hljs-built_in">echo</span>.
<span class="hljs-built_in">pause</span>
</code></pre><!----></div></div></div><!----><!----><!----></code-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element><h3 data-path-to-node="10">💡 ¿Cómo Funciona este Script?</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="11"><li><p data-path-to-node="11,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Ubicación Automática (<code data-path-to-node="11,0,0" data-index-in-node="22">%~dp0</code>):</b> No importa desde dónde ejecutes el archivo, siempre detectará la carpeta de tu proyecto.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Mensaje Personalizado:</b> Te pedirá en pantalla que escribas una breve descripción del cambio (por ejemplo: <code data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="105">cambio de iconos</code> o <code data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="124">ajuste de interfaz</code>). Si solo presionas <b data-path-to-node="11,1,0" data-index-in-node="163">ENTER</b>, le asignará una descripción automática.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Ejecución en Cadena:</b> Ejecuta <code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="29">git add</code>, <code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="38">git commit</code> y <code data-path-to-node="11,2,0" data-index-in-node="51">git push</code> en secuencia.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="11,3,0"><b data-path-to-node="11,3,0" data-index-in-node="0">Confirmación Visual:</b> Cambia el color de la consola a verde (<code data-path-to-node="11,3,0" data-index-in-node="60">color 0A</code>) para avisarte de forma clara cuando el despliegue haya finalizado correctamente.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="13">🖱️ ¿Cómo Usarlo?</h3><p data-path-to-node="14">A partir de ahora, cada vez que hagas cambios en <code data-path-to-node="14" data-index-in-node="49">frontend/app.py</code> o <code data-path-to-node="14" data-index-in-node="67">backend/main.py</code>:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="15"><li><p data-path-to-node="15,0,0">Guarda los archivos en VS Code (<code data-path-to-node="15,0,0" data-index-in-node="32">Ctrl + S</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,1,0">Ve a tu Explorador de Archivos de Windows, busca el archivo <b data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="60"><code data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="60">actualizar.bat</code></b> y dale <b data-path-to-node="15,1,0" data-index-in-node="82">Doble Clic</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="15,2,0">Presiona <b data-path-to-node="15,2,0" data-index-in-node="9">ENTER</b> ¡y listo! Tu web pública se actualizará automáticamente en la nube.</p></li></ol></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-footer complete gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><election-info-disclaimer _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c81433311="" style="display: none;" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></election-info-disclaimer><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3877821886="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c33598