ntent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_4a0b213efde6223a" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_4a0b213efde6223a" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><h3 data-path-to-node="0">🎬 ¡Excelente Elección de Animación!</h3><p data-path-to-node="1">Esa animación de IconScout ("Hojas de árboles cayendo" / Brote creciendo) encaja <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="81">perfectamente</b> con el concepto del <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="115">3. Brote Explorador</b>.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">Para extraer el enlace JSON directo y colocarlo en el código de tu aplicación, sigue estos pasos:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="4">🛠️ Paso a Paso para Obtener el Link JSON</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="5"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Haz Clic en "Descargar":</b> En la página de IconScout donde estás viendo la animación, presiona el botón verde grande <b data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="115"><code data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="115">Descargar</code></b> (o <i data-path-to-node="5,0,0" data-index-in-node="128">Download</i>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Selecciona el Formato Lottie JSON:</b> En el menú desplegable que se abre, elige la opción <b data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="87"><code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="87">Lottie JSON</code></b> o <b data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="101"><code data-path-to-node="5,1,0" data-index-in-node="101">dotLottie</code></b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,2,0" data-index-in-node="0">Obtener el Enlace Público:</b></p><ul data-path-to-node="5,2,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0,0">Si la plataforma te da la opción <b data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="33"><code data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="33">Copy Asset Link</code></b> o <b data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="51"><code data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="51">Embed URL</code></b>, cópiala directamente.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,0">Si se descarga un archivo <code data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="26">.json</code> a tu computadora:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,1"><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,1,0,0">Ve a <response-element class="no-md" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c182818903="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c182818903="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c1623084949="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4a0b213efde6223a&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c5d40269a6639ae3&quot;,null,null,&quot;es&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" href="https://lottiefiles.com/preview" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ6gE">LottieFiles.com/preview</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,1,1,0">Arrastra y suelta el archivo JSON que acabas de descargar.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,1,2,0">Copia el <b data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="9">Lottie Asset URL</b> que te genera (un enlace que termina en <code data-path-to-node="5,2,1,1,1,2,0" data-index-in-node="66">.json</code>).</p></li></ol></li></ul></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="7">💻 Cómo Inyectar la URL en <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="27">frontend/app.py</code></h3><p data-path-to-node="8">Una vez que tengas el enlace (tendrá un formato tipo <code data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="53">[https://lottie.host/.../animacion.json](https://lottie.host/.../animacion.json)</code> o parecido), solo debes reemplazar la línea correspondiente en tu diccionario <code data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="212">mapeo_bio</code> dentro de <code data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="232">frontend/app.py</code>:</p><response-element class="no-md" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3875502131="" class="ng-tns-c3875502131-73 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3875502131-73 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_4a0b213efde6223a&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,&quot;rc_c5d40269a6639ae3&quot;,null,null,&quot;es&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,1]]" style="display: block;" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ6wE"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3875502131-73"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3875502131-73"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-emphasized-body-m ng-tns-c38