ound" jslog="173900;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="1"><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header ng-tns-c3359829210-60 ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header-controls ng-tns-c3359829210-60"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="ng-tns-c3359829210-60 tts ng-trigger ng-trigger-singleResponseEnter ng-star-inserted" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="single-draft-response-container ng-tns-c3359829210-60"><!----></div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header-status ng-tns-c3359829210-60"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header-processing-state ng-tns-c3359829210-60"></div></div></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="presented-response-container ng-tns-c3359829210-60" jslog="283401;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="2"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3359829210-60"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3359829210-60"><!----><thinking-overlay _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c123358160="" class="enable-luminous-fast-follows ng-star-inserted"><!----></thinking-overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted">Gemini ha dicho</h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2691161566="" data-message-id="msg-1784851430121-9" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_b5378d461359748d" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_b5378d461359748d" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><h3 data-path-to-node="0">🛠️ ¡Sí, se puede extraer directo desde el código!</h3><p data-path-to-node="1">Analizando tu captura de pantalla (<code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="35">image_593641.png</code>), estás viendo la pestaña <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="78">Details</b>. Para no tener que pelear inspeccionando el código HTML a la derecha, LottieFiles tiene una pestaña dedicada que te da la URL directa en <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="223">1 solo clic</b>:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="3">🟢 Método Oficial de 1 Clic (Sin inspeccionar código)</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="4"><li><p data-path-to-node="4,0,0">En la página donde estás parado, mira justo al lado del botón <b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="62">Details</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,1,0">Haz clic en la pestaña que dice <b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="32"><code data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="32">Asset &amp; Embed</code></b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,2,0">Verás una casilla con un enlace que termina en <code data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="47">.json</code> (o un botón que dice <b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="74">Copy Lottie URL</b> / <b data-path-to-node="4,2,0" data-index-in-node="92">Copy Asset Link</b>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,3,0">Copia ese enlace y pégalo en tu código Python.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="6">🕵️‍♂️ Método Hack/Dev: Extraerlo desde la Consola del Navegador</h3><p data-path-to-node="7">Si prefieres sacarlo directamente con las herramientas de desarrollador que tienes abiertas a la derecha en la captura:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="8"><li><p data-path-to-node="8,0,0">Ve a la pestaña <b data-path-to-node="8,0,0" data-index-in-node="16">Network</b> (Red) en la ventana del inspector a la derecha.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,1,0">En el filtro de búsqueda de Network, escribe: <code data-path-to-node="8,1,0" data-index-in-node="46">json</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,2,0">Recarga la página (<code data-path-to-node="8,2,0" data-index-in-node="19">F5</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="8,3,0">Verás aparecer un archivo que termina en <code data-path-to-node="8,3,0" data-index-in-node="41">.json</code> o con código de animación. Haz clic derecho sobre él -&gt; <b data-path-to-node="8,3,0" data-index-in-node="103">Copy -&gt; Copy link address</b>.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="10">📋 ¿Cuál es la estructura del link que necesitas?</h3><p data-path-to-node="11">El enlace extraído debe verse exactamente así:
<code data-path-to-node="11" data-index-in-node="47">[https://assets-v2.lottiefiles.com/mottos/.../animacion.json](https://assets-v2.lottiefiles.com/mottos/.../animacion.json)</code> o <code data-path-to-node="11" data-index-in-node="172">[https://lottie.host/.../file.json](https://lottie.host/.../file.json)</code></p><p data-path-to-node="12">Esa URL que copiaste es la que colocas directamente en la tupla de la fase correspondiente dentro del archivo <b data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="110"><code data-path-to-node="12" data-index-in-node="110">frontend/app.py</code></b>.</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-footer complete gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><election-info-disclaimer _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c81433311="" style="display: none;" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></election-info-disclaimer><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3877821886="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3359829210-60 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" footer="" class="hide-on-print ng-tns-c36277369-61 ng-tns-c3359829210-60 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" _nghost-ng-c36277369=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-61"><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-61 ng-star-inserted"><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" _nghost-ng-c3123964857="" class="ng-tns-c36277369-61 luminous-theme ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3123