ted" _nghost-ng-c2691161566="" data-message-id="msg-1784852730765-11" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_c66456491cecd9c0" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_c66456491cecd9c0" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0"><b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="0">No, ese no es el enlace de la animación.</b></p><p data-path-to-node="1">El enlace que ves en la imagen (<code data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="32">[https://lottiefiles.com/assets/url-dVDIYupe.js](https://lottiefiles.com/assets/url-dVDIYupe.js)</code>) corresponde a un <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="147">archivo JavaScript de soporte de la plataforma LottieFiles</b> (utilizado internamente por el sitio web para manejar la validación o localización de URLs en el cliente), no al recurso gráfico en sí.</p><h2 data-path-to-node="3">Modelado de Tipos de Recursos en DevTools</h2><p data-path-to-node="4">Para identificar correctamente lo que estás buscando, ten en cuenta la siguiente estructura de archivos:</p><div class="horizontal-scroll-wrapper"><div class="table-block-component"><response-element class="no-md" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><table-block _nghost-ng-c4245566456="" class="enable-luminous-table-block ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4245566456="" class="table-block has-export-button new-table-style is-at-scroll-start is-at-scroll-end"><div _ngcontent-ng-c4245566456="" not-end-of-paragraph="" class="table-content md-content" jslog="275421;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ3ecQahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQqAI"><table data-path-to-node="5"><thead><tr><th><span data-path-to-node="5,0,0,0">Tipo de Archivo</span></th><th><span data-path-to-node="5,0,1,0">Extensión típica</span></th><th><span data-path-to-node="5,0,2,0">Descripción / Propósito</span></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="5,1,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,1,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Código Frontend (No es la animación)</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,1,1,0"><code data-path-to-node="5,1,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">.js</code></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,1,2,0">Scripts de lógica del sitio (como el que seleccionaste).</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="5,2,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,2,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Animación Lottie (JSON)</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0"><code data-path-to-node="5,2,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">.json</code></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,2,2,0">Estructura vectorial pura de la animación.</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="5,3,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,3,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Animación Lottie (dotLottie)</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,3,1,0"><code data-path-to-node="5,3,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">.lottie</code></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,3,2,0">Formato comprimido optimizado para Lottie.</span></td></tr><tr><td><span data-path-to-node="5,4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="5,4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">Media / Asset</b></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,4,1,0"><code data-path-to-node="5,4,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">.gif</code>, <code data-path-to-node="5,4,1,0" data-index-in-node="6">.mp4</code>, <code data-path-to-node="5,4,1,0" data-index-in-node="12">.svg</code></span></td><td><span data-path-to-node="5,4,2,0">Renderizados alternativos del recurso visual.</span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c4245566456="" hide-from-message-actions="" class="table-footer hide-on-print hide-from-message-actions"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c4245566456="" tabindex="0" gemmenutrigger="" cdkoverlayorigin="" theme="lm" type="tonal" arialabel="Más opciones" gemtooltip="Más opciones" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger overflow-menu-button gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-tonal lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2005957155="" aria-disabled="false" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ng-menu-a69846-38" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-57" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" maticonbutton="" matbadgeposition="after" class="mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-icon-button mat-mdc-button-base mat-badge mat-unthemed _mat-animation-noopable mat-badge-overlap mat-badge-above mat-badge-after mat-badge-small mat-badge-hidden ng-star-inserted" mat-ripple-loader-uninitialized="" mat-ripple-loader-class-name="mat-mdc-button-ripple" mat-ripple-loader-centered="" aria-label="Más opciones" jslog="305704;track:generic_click,impression"><span class="mat-mdc-button-persistent-ripple mdc-icon-button__ripple"></span><gem-icon _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" _nghost-ng-c1721858669=""><mat-icon _ngcontent-ng-c1721858669="" role="img" class="mat-icon notranslate lm-icon-l lumi-symbols mat-ligature-font mat-icon-no-color ng-star-inserted" aria-hidden="true" data-mat-icon-type="font" data-mat-icon-name="more_horiz" data-mat-icon-namespace="lumi-symbols" fonticon="more_horiz"></mat-icon><!----><!----><!----></gem-icon><!----><span class="mat-focus-indicator"></span><span class="mat-mdc-button-touch-target"></span></button><!----><!----></gem-icon-button><!----><gem-popover _ngcontent-ng-c4245566456="" _nghost-ng-c2385589692="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></gem-popover><!----><!----></div></div><!----></table-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></div></div><h2 data-path-to-node="7">¿Cómo encontrar el link correcto?</h2><p data-path-to-node="8">Si estás intentando extraer la animación desde las <b data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="51">DevTools (F12)</b> del navegador:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="9"><li><p data-path-to-node="9,0,0">Ve a la pestaña <b data-path-to-node="9,0,0" data-index-in-node="16">Network (Red)</b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,1,0">Filtra por <b data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="11">Fetch/XHR</b> en lugar de ver todos los archivos o scripts (<code data-path-to-node="9,1,0" data-index-in-node="67">JS</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,2,0">Busca peticiones que terminen en <b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="33"><code data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="33">.json</code></b> o <b data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="41"><code data-path-to-node="9,2,0" data-index-in-node="41">.lottie</code></b>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="9,3,0">Alternativamente, si buscas el GIF/MP4 directamente, revisa la pestaña <b data-path-to-node="9,3,0" data-index-in-node="71">Img</b> o <b data-path-to-node="9,3,0" data-index-in-node="77">Media</b>.</p></li></ol><blockquote data-path-to-node="10"><p data-path-to-node="10,0"><b data-path-to-node="10,0" data-index-in-node="0">Nota:</b> Si la animación Lottie está incrustada en la página mediante el reproductor oficial, suele realizar una llamada a un endpoint de LottieFiles que entrega la data en formato JSON (<code data-path-to-node="10,0" data-index-in-node="184">[https://assets-v.lottiefiles.com/.../animacion.json](https://assets-v.lottiefiles.com/.../animacion.json)</code>).</p></blockquote></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-footer gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><election-info-disclaimer _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c81433311="" style="display: none;" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></election-info-disclaimer><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3877821886="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3359829210-82 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" footer="" class="hide-on-print ng-tns-c36277369-83 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" _nghost-ng-c36277369="" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-83"><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-83 ng-star-inserted"><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" _nghost-ng-c3123964857="" class="ng-tns-c36277369-83 luminous-theme ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3123964857="" tabindex="-1" theme="lm" type="onSurface" arialabel="Buena respuesta" gemtooltip="Buena respuesta" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2005957155="" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-25" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" maticonbutton="" matbadgeposition="after" class="