><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3359829210-114"><!----><thinking-overlay _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c123358160="" class="enable-luminous-fast-follows ng-star-inserted"><!----></thinking-overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted">Gemini ha dicho</h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-text processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2691161566="" data-message-id="msg-1784854351964-15" style="height: auto;"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_745c0d467c33acee" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_745c0d467c33acee" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><h3 data-path-to-node="0">🔍 Diagnóstico Visual: ¿Por qué la tarjeta cambia pero la imagen no?</h3><p data-path-to-node="1">En el video se observa perfectamente lo que ocurre:</p><ul data-path-to-node="2"><li><p data-path-to-node="2,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="2,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">La tarjeta azul sí funciona:</b> Cambia de <code data-path-to-node="2,0,0" data-index-in-node="39">1. Semilla</code> a <code data-path-to-node="2,0,0" data-index-in-node="52">2. Brote Menor</code> y luego a <code data-path-to-node="2,0,0" data-index-in-node="77">3. Brote Explorador</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="2,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="2,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">La imagen no cambia:</b> Se queda mostrando permanentemente el brote verde con dos hojas.</p></li></ul><p data-path-to-node="3">Esto sucede por <b data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="16">dos razones técnicas</b> en <code data-path-to-node="3" data-index-in-node="40">streamlit-lottie</code>:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="4"><li><p data-path-to-node="4,0,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="0">La función <code data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="11">cargar_lottie</code> está en caché (<code data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="40">@st.cache_data</code>):</b> Si las URLs apuntan a recursos inaccesibles o si la respuesta falla internamente, la función retorna <code data-path-to-node="4,0,0" data-index-in-node="158">None</code> de forma cacheada y la interfaz cae al fallback (el brote estático).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="4,1,0"><b data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="0">Las URLs de los paquetes viejos de LottieFiles están rotas (<code data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="60">lf20_...</code>):</b> Las URLs tipo <code data-path-to-node="4,1,0" data-index-in-node="85">[https://assets9.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_sprout_growing.json](https://assets9.lottiefiles.com/packages/lf20_sprout_growing.json)</code> fueron retiradas por LottieFiles hace un tiempo y responden con error HTTP 404. Al fallar la descarga, la app renderiza el mismo ícono de contingencia para todas las fases.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="6">🛠️ Solución Definitiva (URLs CDN Vivas de <code data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="43">lottie.host</code>)</h3><p data-path-to-node="7">Para solucionar esto de forma permanente y garantizada, reemplazaremos el diccionario <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="86">mapeo_bio</code> con <b data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="100">URLs activas en el nuevo CDN público de Lottie (<code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="148">lottie.host</code>)</b> y <b data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="163">forzaremos la actualización del componente con un <code data-path-to-node="7" data-index-in-node="213">key</code> dinámico</b>.</p><p data-path-to-node="8">Sustituye la sección del <b data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="25">Visor Gráfico del Árbol</b> en <code data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="52">frontend/app.py</code> por este bloque:</p><response-element class="no-md" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><code-block _nghost-ng-c3875502131="" class="ng-tns-c3875502131-121 enable-luminous-code-block ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="code-block ng-tns-c3875502131-121 ng-animate-disabled ng-trigger ng-trigger-codeBlockRevealAnimation" jslog="223238;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_745c0d467c33acee&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,&quot;rc_f32ca3c523594a56&quot;,null,null,&quot;es&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" style="display: block;" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQhtANahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQlQM"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="formatted-code-block-internal-container ng-tns-c3875502131-121"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="animated-opacity ng-tns-c3875502131-121"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="code-block-decoration header-formatted gds-emphasized-body-m ng-tns-c3875502131-121 ng-star-inserted" style=""><span _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="ng-tns-c3875502131-121">Python</span><div _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" class="buttons ng-tns-c3875502131-121 ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3875502131="" tabindex="-1" type="onSurface" size="small" fonticonname="arrow_circle_down" theme="lm" arialabel="Descargar código" gemtooltip="Descargar código" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger download-button ng-tns-c3875502131-121 gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c200