overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted">Gemini ha dicho</h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2691161566="" style="height: auto;" data-message-id="msg-1784857099642-22"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_ca293602e23d55e1" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_ca293602e23d55e1" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">¡Jajaja, con razón te salió raro! Te fuiste para otro lado del internet.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">En la captura que me envías terminaste en <b data-path-to-node="1" data-index-in-node="42">Scribd</b>, que es una plataforma para leer libros, documentos en PDF y ensayos. Ahí nunca vas a encontrar una animación web; solo vas a encontrar manuales de jardinería.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">La plataforma oficial y correcta para buscar este tipo de recursos es <b data-path-to-node="2" data-index-in-node="70">LottieFiles</b>.</p><h3 data-path-to-node="4">🟢 El Enlace Correcto a la Galería</h3><p data-path-to-node="5">Haz clic exactamente aquí para ir a la galería de animaciones gratuitas de plantas creciendo:</p><p data-path-to-node="6">👉 <b data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="3"><response-element class="no-md" ng-version="0.0.0-PLACEHOLDER"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><link-block _nghost-ng-c182818903="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><a _ngcontent-ng-c182818903="" target="_blank" rel="noopener" externallink="" _nghost-ng-c1623084949="" jslog="197247;track:generic_click,impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_ca293602e23d55e1&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,&quot;rc_1bf2dded5e3adb93&quot;,null,null,&quot;es&quot;,null,1,null,null,1,0]]" href="https://www.google.com/search?q=https://lottiefiles.com/search%3Fq%3Dplant%2520growing%26price%3Dfree" class="ng-star-inserted" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQ_4QMahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ5gQ">Buscador Oficial de LottieFiles: Plant Growing (Gratis)</a><!----></link-block><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></response-element></b></p><h3 data-path-to-node="8">📥 Pasos para descargar el archivo <code data-path-to-node="8" data-index-in-node="35">.json</code></h3><p data-path-to-node="9">Una vez que estés en esa página correcta, haz lo siguiente:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="10"><li><p data-path-to-node="10,0,0">Haz clic en la animación que más te guste.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="10,1,0">En la ventana del reproductor que se abre, busca el botón <b data-path-to-node="10,1,0" data-index-in-node="58">Download</b> (Descargar) o un ícono de flecha ⬇️ en la esquina superior derecha.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="10,2,0">Se abrirá un pequeño menú. Haz clic obligatoriamente en la opción que dice <b data-path-to-node="10,2,0" data-index-in-node="75">Lottie JSON</b> (o <i data-path-to-node="10,2,0" data-index-in-node="90">JSON format</i>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="10,3,0">Se abrirá la ventana de tu computador para guardar el archivo.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="10,4,0">Guárdalo dentro de tu carpeta <code data-path-to-node="10,4,0" data-index-in-node="30">frontend/assets/</code> y ponle el nombre correspondiente (por ejemplo, <b data-path-to-node="10,4,0" data-index-in-node="95"><code data-path-to-node="10,4,0" data-index-in-node="95">brote_menor.json</code></b>).</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="11">¡Inténtalo en ese enlace y verás que ahora sí te descargas la animación correcta y no un PDF de agricultura!</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-footer has-thoughts gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><election-info-disclaimer _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c81433311="" style="display: none;" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></election-info-disclaimer><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3877821886="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3359829210-169 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" footer="" class="hide-on-print ng-tns-c36277369-170 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" _nghost-ng-c36277369="" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-170"><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-170 ng-star-inserted"><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c