r _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3359829210="" class="ng-tns-c3359829210-172 reduced-bottom-padding enable-lr26-response-chrome-updates enable-luminous-sources ng-star-inserted" jslog="188576;track:impression,attention;BardVeMetadataKey:[[&quot;r_309d5647f2284d66&quot;,&quot;c_9f1515e3a1ed4f84&quot;,null,null,null,null,null,null,1,null,null,null,0]];mutable:true" data-hveid="0" decode-data-ved="1" data-ved="0CAAQoMELahgKEwjP76DPgeqVAxUAAAAAHQAAAAAQ7wQ"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container response-container-with-gpi ng-tns-c3359829210-172 no-background" jslog="173900;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="1"><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header ng-tns-c3359829210-172 ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header-controls ng-tns-c3359829210-172"><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="ng-tns-c3359829210-172 tts ng-trigger ng-trigger-singleResponseEnter ng-star-inserted" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="single-draft-response-container ng-tns-c3359829210-172"><!----></div></div><!----><!----></div><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header-status ng-tns-c3359829210-172"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-header-processing-state ng-tns-c3359829210-172"></div></div></div><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="presented-response-container ng-tns-c3359829210-172" jslog="283401;track:impression,attention" data-hveid="2"><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-content ng-tns-c3359829210-172 has-thoughts"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-content ng-tns-c3359829210-172"><!----><thinking-overlay _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c123358160="" class="enable-luminous-fast-follows ng-star-inserted"><!----></thinking-overlay><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-label-announcer" aria-live="off" aria-busy="false"><!----><!----><h2 _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="cdk-visually-hidden screen-reader-model-response-label ng-star-inserted">Gemini ha dicho</h2><!----><!----></div><!----><structured-content-container _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="model-response-text has-thoughts processing-state-visible ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2691161566="" style="height: auto;" data-message-id="msg-1784858061196-23"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" class="container"><message-content _ngcontent-ng-c2691161566="" _nghost-ng-c437757345="" id="message-content-id-r_309d5647f2284d66" class="ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c437757345="" inline-copy-host="" class="markdown markdown-main-panel enable-luminous-fast-follows enable-updated-hr-color md-content stronger" id="model-response-message-contentr_309d5647f2284d66" aria-busy="false" aria-live="off" dir="ltr" style="--animation-duration: 400ms; --fade-animation-function: ease-out;"><p data-path-to-node="0">¡Ese enlace es <b data-path-to-node="0" data-index-in-node="15">perfecto</b>! Es exactamente el archivo en bruto que necesitas.</p><p data-path-to-node="1">Como es un enlace directo al código del archivo, guardarlo en tu computador es súper fácil y rápido. Sigue uno de estos dos métodos:</p><h3 data-path-to-node="2">⚡ Método 1: El más rápido (Sin abrir el enlace)</h3><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="3"><li><p data-path-to-node="3,0,0">Haz <b data-path-to-node="3,0,0" data-index-in-node="4">Clic Derecho</b> exactamente sobre el enlace que me acabas de pasar.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,1,0">En el menú que se abre, selecciona la opción <b data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="45"><code data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="45">Guardar enlace como...</code></b> (o <i data-path-to-node="3,1,0" data-index-in-node="71">Save link as...</i>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,2,0">Busca la carpeta de tu proyecto (<code data-path-to-node="3,2,0" data-index-in-node="33">HistoriasQueInspiran -&gt; frontend -&gt; assets</code>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,3,0">En la casilla de nombre, bórralo todo y ponle el nombre de la fase en la que lo quieras usar (por ejemplo: <b data-path-to-node="3,3,0" data-index-in-node="107"><code data-path-to-node="3,3,0" data-index-in-node="107">brote_menor.json</code></b> o <b data-path-to-node="3,3,0" data-index-in-node="126"><code data-path-to-node="3,3,0" data-index-in-node="126">arbol_joven_creativo.json</code></b>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="3,4,0">Dale a <b data-path-to-node="3,4,0" data-index-in-node="7">Guardar</b>.</p></li></ol><h3 data-path-to-node="5">💻 Método 2: Si ya le diste clic y lo abriste</h3><p data-path-to-node="6">Si le diste clic normal y se te abrió una pestaña nueva en el navegador llena de texto raro y llaves <code data-path-to-node="6" data-index-in-node="101">{ }</code>:</p><ol start="1" data-path-to-node="7"><li><p data-path-to-node="7,0,0">Haz <b data-path-to-node="7,0,0" data-index-in-node="4">Clic Derecho</b> en cualquier espacio en blanco de esa misma pantalla.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="7,1,0">Selecciona <b data-path-to-node="7,1,0" data-index-in-node="11"><code data-path-to-node="7,1,0" data-index-in-node="11">Guardar como...</code></b> (o <i data-path-to-node="7,1,0" data-index-in-node="30">Save as...</i>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="7,2,0">Busca tu carpeta <code data-path-to-node="7,2,0" data-index-in-node="17">HistoriasQueInspiran -&gt; frontend -&gt; assets</code>.</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="7,3,0">Ponle el nombre de la fase en minúsculas (ej. <b data-path-to-node="7,3,0" data-index-in-node="46"><code data-path-to-node="7,3,0" data-index-in-node="46">brote_explorador.json</code></b>).</p></li><li><p data-path-to-node="7,4,0">Dale a <b data-path-to-node="7,4,0" data-index-in-node="7">Guardar</b>.</p></li></ol><p data-path-to-node="8">Una vez guardado ahí, tu código (el que implementamos hace un momento) lo leerá automáticamente y la animación cobrará vida en tu plataforma web.</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="response-footer has-thoughts gap complete"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><election-info-disclaimer _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c81433311="" style="display: none;" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></election-info-disclaimer><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" _nghost-ng-c3877821886="" class="ng-star-inserted" style=""><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c3359829210="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c3359829210-172 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c3377849098="" footer="" class="hide-on-print ng-tns-c36277369-173 ng-star-inserted hide-action-bar" _nghost-ng-c36277369="" style=""><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-173"><div _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c36277369-173 ng-star-inserted"><thumb-up-button _ngcontent-ng-c36277369="" _nghost-ng-c3123964857="" class="ng-tns-c36277369-173 luminous-theme ng-star-inserted"><gem-icon-button _ngcontent-ng-c3123964857="" tabindex="-1" theme="lm" type="onSurface" arialabel="Buena respuesta" gemtooltip="Buena respuesta" data-test-id="thumb-up-button" class="mat-mdc-tooltip-trigger gem-button gem-button-badge-size-small gem-button-size-small gem-button-type-on-surface lm-enabled ng-star-inserted" _nghost-ng-c2005957155="" aria-describedby="cdk-describedby-message-ng-1-25" cdk-describedby-host="ng-1"><!----><!----><button _ngcontent-ng-c2005957155="" m